      <title>高盛：美元并未进入大幅贬值区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/dollar-not-in-zone-of-aggressive-depreciation-goldman-s-trivedi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛全球外汇和利率主管卡马科什亚·特里维迪 (Kamakshya Trivedi) 表示：“宽松政策即将在你身边的央行实施。”他解释了为什么美联储降息将允许新兴市场和全球央行实施宽松政策，从而限制美元疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/dollar-not-in-zone-of-aggressive-depreciation-goldman-s-trivedi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 12:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
